## 🔍 **Quick Check Sebelum Commit**

Buat script `check_errors.bat`:
```batch
@echo off
echo Running Pylint...
pylint backend/routes/reports/annual.py

echo Running mypy...
mypy backend/routes/reports/annual.py

echo Running Black (check only)...
black --check backend/routes/reports/annual.py

echo Done!
```

